Title: Two-Faced
Plot: To Gibbs' displeasure, Special Agent E.J. Barrett returns to lead the investigation of a seaman's death that may be connected to a series of port-related murders. Meanwhile, Ziva finally introduces her boyfriend, Ray, to the team.
GuestStars: Sarah Jane Morris, Ryan Carnes, Enrique Murciano, Marque Richardson II, Nicholas James, Roy Jackson, Erin Ross
